com.complexible.common.openrdf.model

Interface FunctionalGraph

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<org.openrdf.model.Statement>, org.openrdf.model.Graph, Iterable<org.openrdf.model.Statement>, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExtGraph

    public interface FunctionalGraph
extends org.openrdf.model.Graph

    Convenience interface for a Sesame Graph for applying some of the Guava functional objects to a Graph.

    Since:
    0.8
